==English==

===Noun===
'''database''' (''plural'' '''[[databases]]'''); (''older spellings'': '''[[data base]]''', '''[[data-base]]''')

# A collection of (usually) organized [[information]] in a regular structure, usually but not necessarily in a [[machine-readable]] format accessed by a [[computer]]. E.G. "I have a database of all my contacts in my [[filoFAX]]."
# A software program for storing, retrieving and manipulating a database(1). E.G. "Which database do you use, MySql or Access?" 
# A combination of (1) and (2). 

